&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://note-1311335427.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/images/image-20230710111411877.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20230710111411877&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
